ement-Jesus-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DaddyYankee-retirement-Jesus-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daddy-yankee">洋基老爹</a>表示，他将退出音乐界，将一生奉献给耶稣。</p><p>据<a href="https://people.com/daddy-yankee-retiring-to-devote-life-to-christianity-8411537" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》杂志</em></a>报道，这位说唱歌手和雷鬼艺术家最近在波多黎各圣胡安的 Coliseo José Miguel Agrelot 竞技场的舞台上谈到了他的计划。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/ozuna-anuel-aa-los-dioses-cardi-b-latin-music-best-in-world-2871822">波多黎各流行偶像奥祖纳：“拉丁音乐是世界上最好的音乐！”</a></strong></li></ul><p> “我的朋友们，这是我一生中最重要的一天。我想分享它......因为成功的生活与有目标的生活不同，”他在最后一场音乐会上告诉观众（翻译自西班牙语）。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" style="background: #FFF; border: 0; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width: 540px; min-width: 326px; padding: 0; width: calc(100% - 2px);" data-instgrm-captioned="" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C0a5YMJgfGz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14"><div style="padding: 16px;"><p></p><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style="background-color: #f4f4f4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display: block; height: 50px; margin: 0 auto 12px; width: 50px;"></div><div style="padding-top: 8px;"><div style="color: #3897f0; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; f